      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and the rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, riding on a perfectly damped suspension that maintains factory geometry. Finished in a concours-level exterior with a flawless cabin, this is a turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
